    <briefdescription>
<para>This class allows to read any document of the predefined list of formats according to the available list of readers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The list of readers is set via the class constructor. The first suitable reader is used for parsing (the one whose method :meth:<computeroutput>~dedoc.readers.BaseReader.can_read</computeroutput> returns True), \ so the order of the given readers is important. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
